  "detailed_description": "<strong>You are an employee working overtime for Genesis, a genome research facility. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/a633a90507005a8e6951ce746b4527e7.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=106 /></span><br><br><br>You are tasked with activating location trackers on four vehicles belonging to a competitor. Navigate through an underground parking lot in search of the vehicles. <strong>Find all four vehicles to escape from the parking lot.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/441cb5ca4f37ea0d70c9b8ff8b34d32f.poster.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/441cb5ca4f37ea0d70c9b8ff8b34d32f.webm?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/441cb5ca4f37ea0d70c9b8ff8b34d32f.mp4?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Be careful; there are abnormals sent to intercept you. Do not fight them; they have unique abilities.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/9e7cb536f3da3f9e32bbe7a8b6553d72.poster.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/9e7cb536f3da3f9e32bbe7a8b6553d72.webm?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/9e7cb536f3da3f9e32bbe7a8b6553d72.mp4?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>Below Level is a first-person survival horror game inspired by the liminal atmosphere of underground parking spaces. <br><br>There are a total of six unique abnormals, each with carefully crafted perception systems. The player must figure out what type of perception each abnormal possesses in order to avoid them (ie vision, hearing, or both).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/b5edbf877c41720e51a9763508c009e3.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=106 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>You are an employee working overtime for Genesis, a genome research facility. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/a633a90507005a8e6951ce746b4527e7.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=106 /></span><br><br><br>You are tasked with activating location trackers on four vehicles belonging to a competitor. Navigate through an underground parking lot in search of the vehicles. <strong>Find all four vehicles to escape from the parking lot.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/441cb5ca4f37ea0d70c9b8ff8b34d32f.poster.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/441cb5ca4f37ea0d70c9b8ff8b34d32f.webm?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/441cb5ca4f37ea0d70c9b8ff8b34d32f.mp4?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Be careful; there are abnormals sent to intercept you. Do not fight them; they have unique abilities.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/9e7cb536f3da3f9e32bbe7a8b6553d72.poster.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/9e7cb536f3da3f9e32bbe7a8b6553d72.webm?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/9e7cb536f3da3f9e32bbe7a8b6553d72.mp4?t=1760564418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br>Below Level is a first-person survival horror game inspired by the liminal atmosphere of underground parking spaces. <br><br>There are a total of six unique abnormals, each with carefully crafted perception systems. The player must figure out what type of perception each abnormal possesses in order to avoid them (ie vision, hearing, or both).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963740/extras/b5edbf877c41720e51a9763508c009e3.avif?t=1760564418\" width=640 height=106 /></span>",
